subject: New messages posted
author: Misty
full_text:
Hello everyone. I posted a few files from my recent sweep tuning 
session. I will try and post more from it later when I get time. There 
was one very lengthy message that seemed to be a higher level 'poetic' 
type voice. Also some messages involving a new member to our group. 
It's up to him if he wants to share his experiences. However I did post 
the one file with his name because it has some significant meaning to 
me that I explained on the file post there. It reminded me of something 
Frank Sumption sent me years ago when I was a newbie and had the same 
effect on me that it had on the new member.

http://www.esnips.com/web/SweepTuningEVP

Misty Dawn
